title: Return on equity of BNP Paribas 2003 to 2018
summary: In general Return on equity has fallen over the Year.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2010 and 2011.
The highest Return on equity, of value 12.3 was reached at Year 2010
Minimum Return on equity about 6.1 was reached at Year 2013
